&lt;p&gt;Ability to work on septic and commercial sewer systems&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Perform plumbing preventative maintenance service for contract customers&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to work with tablet-based service ticket software system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Ability to work overtime in peak seasons and join the plumber on-call rotation&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Education/Experience&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;High School diploma or GED&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;em&gt;Preferred Qualifications&amp;nbsp;&lt;/em&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Installation and repair of commercial rough plumbing and plumbing fixtures including sinks, toilets, bathtubs, water heaters, and water softeners&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with installation and repair of water treatment equipment, piping and controls&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Experience with installation and repair of underground storm sanitary and water piping system&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Professional, ethical, and a team player willing to grow with the company&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Journeyman plumber preferred&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Knowledge of plumbing codes&lt;/p&gt;
