&lt;p&gt;Competitive salary, commensurate with experience&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Company paid vacation and holidays&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Company health care, vision, &amp;amp; dental benefits&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;401k plan with Company match&lt;/p&gt;
